  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Base Building</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design, create, and decorate your very own space station. (<i>Base... The final frontier!)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/c80755924ed6e3bddda69ad200380e65.poster.avif?t=1770352417\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/c80755924ed6e3bddda69ad200380e65.webm?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/c80755924ed6e3bddda69ad200380e65.mp4?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >   <strong>On-Planet Missions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect powerups and materials for your space station through challenging levels and boss fights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/3f598026e2b0b9e92ee65a53ff12b7da.poster.avif?t=1770352417\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/3f598026e2b0b9e92ee65a53ff12b7da.webm?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/3f598026e2b0b9e92ee65a53ff12b7da.mp4?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Split-Screen Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to four players can join the fun in co-op or vs. mode.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/33a7c295d73581eec14a8f98a0596f54.poster.avif?t=1770352417\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/33a7c295d73581eec14a8f98a0596f54.webm?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/33a7c295d73581eec14a8f98a0596f54.mp4?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Interactive NPCs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NPCs teach you how to build, train you in combat, and offer decorations for your personalized base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/aa80a7ce78f852a180e018429ecd2273.poster.avif?t=1770352417\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/aa80a7ce78f852a180e018429ecd2273.webm?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/aa80a7ce78f852a180e018429ecd2273.mp4?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build your space station</strong> - Power it up. Fight to protect it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive Events </strong>- Hazardous asteroid fields, dangerous enemies, and trading merchants visit your base.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Items & PowerUps</strong> - Collect items to power up your bot's attacks, building abilities, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collectables </strong>- Collect PowerStones, decorations, secret codes, and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple, One-Button Building</strong> - Easy to pick up, hard to put down.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Split-Screen Multiplayer </strong>- Up to four players across several game modes.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Base Building</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design, create, and decorate your very own space station. (<i>Base... The final frontier!)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/c80755924ed6e3bddda69ad200380e65.poster.avif?t=1770352417\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/c80755924ed6e3bddda69ad200380e65.webm?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/c80755924ed6e3bddda69ad200380e65.mp4?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >   <strong>On-Planet Missions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect powerups and materials for your space station through challenging levels and boss fights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/3f598026e2b0b9e92ee65a53ff12b7da.poster.avif?t=1770352417\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/3f598026e2b0b9e92ee65a53ff12b7da.webm?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/3f598026e2b0b9e92ee65a53ff12b7da.mp4?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Split-Screen Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to four players can join the fun in co-op or vs. mode.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/33a7c295d73581eec14a8f98a0596f54.poster.avif?t=1770352417\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/33a7c295d73581eec14a8f98a0596f54.webm?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/33a7c295d73581eec14a8f98a0596f54.mp4?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Interactive NPCs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NPCs teach you how to build, train you in combat, and offer decorations for your personalized base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/aa80a7ce78f852a180e018429ecd2273.poster.avif?t=1770352417\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/aa80a7ce78f852a180e018429ecd2273.webm?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814880/extras/aa80a7ce78f852a180e018429ecd2273.mp4?t=1770352417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build your space station</strong> - Power it up. Fight to protect it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive Events </strong>- Hazardous asteroid fields, dangerous enemies, and trading merchants visit your base.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Items & PowerUps</strong> - Collect items to power up your bot's attacks, building abilities, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collectables </strong>- Collect PowerStones, decorations, secret codes, and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple, One-Button Building</strong> - Easy to pick up, hard to put down.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Split-Screen Multiplayer </strong>- Up to four players across several game modes.</p></li></ul>",
